comment._content: Possibly the same woman as at cdm.sos.state.ga.us/cdm4/item_viewer.php?CISOROOT=/vg2&am... dlg.galileo.usg.edu/meta/html/dlg/vang/meta_dlg_vang_cob7... is a picture of her in the same outfit as here.
